Futu OpenAPI Protocol

This SDK implements a client for the Futu OpenD protocol based on publicly
available API documentation from Futu Holdings Limited. This implementation is
a clean-room reverse engineering effort and does not contain any proprietary
code from Futu Holdings Limited.

Futu OpenAPI documentation is Copyright (c) Futu Holdings Limited.
Official documentation: https://openapi.futunn.com/

